---
title: Sweet Chilli Udon Noodles with Snow Peas, Bok Choy and Roasted Cashews
description: Put your table manners to the side just for tonight – we’re slurping these saucy noodles without any shame. Along with cashews and peanuts for a super nutty crunchy finish, this colourful bowl is perfectly satisfying on a hectic weeknight.
